Introduction

Oh!Bliss (Korean: 오블리스) is a five-member girl group formed by JT Corea Entertainment in 2016. The group made their debut in October 17, 2016 with the single "Bunny Bunny". Their name means a combination of interjection Oh+Bliss hoping to give happiness through their music.
